New Records: Glenn Maxwell scored the fastest century in World Cups (40 balls)
Logan van Beek delivered the most expensive over in men's ODI history
Key Match Events: Glenn Maxwell scored 106 runs in 44 balls
Logan van Beek took 4 wickets for 74 runs in 10 overs
Adam Zampa took 4 wickets for 8 runs in 3 overs
David Warner scored 104 runs in 93 balls
Bas de Leede bowled the most expensive over in men's ODI history
Post-Match Reflections: Glenn Maxwell: 'Not something I set out to do. Just situation of the game. Wanted to put a good platform for the back end and cash in on this ground.'
David Warner: 'Special moment for Maxwell. Great to get the fifty and get the hundred.'
Scott Edwards, Netherlands captain: 'Defending 400, yeah, they've got world-class bowlers and we should've been better today.'
Pat Cummins, Australia captain: 'Just about the complete game. Couldn't be happier.'
Miscellaneous Highlights: A target of 400 was always going to be daunting and all we wanted to see was how Netherlands would respond to the target.
Zampa now has the most wickets at the 2023 WC (13).
This is the largest victory in WC history - 309 runs.
